{"TopicId":119991,"ForumId":36,"TopicTitle":"[1.1.3] BDArmory FPS - A BDArmory Expansion - 0.4 (9-10-16)","CreatedByName":"V8jester","CreatedById":136093,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-02T19:40:59Z","PageNum":10,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"War Eagle 1","CreatedById":67109,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-20T15:51:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222420476\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455977659\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002250907\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SpannerMonkey(smce)\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, SpannerMonkey(smce) said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts the one you haven\u0027t got yet \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut seriously I can\u0027t tell you which one it is, due to the handicap previously mentioned\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E , just a generic pump action thingy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProbably for the next update though as it\u0027s so close to kick out time for v3,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0Mind you with the right folder structure,a later download could be just merged into the main with no real issues\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you want i can give you a list of shotguns that would be cool to add.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"V8jester","CreatedById":136093,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-20T17:02:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222420133\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455944085\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002250907\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SpannerMonkey(smce)\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, SpannerMonkey(smce) said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProperly armed and properly attired for the occasion is the only way to go \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEpic man! I can\u0027t believe we never thought of that!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSee now we need to tweak a cfg to suite a shoty. (Looks like a Mossberg 500 to me)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wonder if you could set up the barrel with multiple \u0022barrels\u0022 which all fire at once. Like the ship guns in NAS. Then offset there alignment to the center of the barrel slightly.\u00A0Then in the cfg turn the affective range way down as well as the Max Deviation way up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-20T17:02:41Z\u0022 title=\u002202/20/2016 05:02  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 20, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by V8jester\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpannerMonkey(smce)","CreatedById":50907,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-20T17:12:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222420741\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455987730\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022136093\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022V8jester\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, V8jester said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEpic man! I can\u0027t believe we never thought of that!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSee now we need to tweak a cfg to suite a shoty. (Looks like a Mossberg 500 to me)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wonder if you could set up the barrel with multiple \u0022barrels\u0022 which all fire at once. Like the ship guns in NAS. Then offset there alignment to the center of the barrel slightly.\u00A0Then in the cfg turn the affective range way down as well as the Max Deviation way up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlready has multiple fire transforms, deviation per transform 1mtr, 500 mtrs max hits around 3sqm\u00A0 or 9 kerbals \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E also has own sound files and a reload anim, i\u0027ll pack one for test later. \u00A0 Currently working on javelin, would like to get it in game and set for test tonight\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"War Eagle 1","CreatedById":67109,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-20T19:56:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m going to be away for a while. Be back tonight\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"V8jester","CreatedById":136093,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-20T21:04:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222420751\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455988346\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002250907\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SpannerMonkey(smce)\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, SpannerMonkey(smce) said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlready has multiple fire transforms, deviation per transform 1mtr, 500 mtrs max hits around 3sqm\u00A0 or 9 kerbals \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E also has own sound files and a reload anim, i\u0027ll pack one for test later. \u00A0 Currently working on javelin, would like to get it in game and set for test tonight\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSee already 10 steps ahead of me \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0I\u0027m working on a new OP video. Nothing too fancy just a \u0022hey looky what these can do\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"V8jester","CreatedById":136093,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-20T22:01:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n0.3 Teaser\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/tKekkfN85ps?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Space Scumbag","CreatedById":70411,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-21T00:06:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice! Can\u0027t wait for it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSome suggestions.\u00A0Maybe make the bullet shells a bit smaller. And how are the sound effect?\u00A0Nothing to hear in the video.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd no new Blaster? Was hoping to see it. Maybe in the future. Anyways, great work guys, this mod\u00A0is getting really good.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"War Eagle 1","CreatedById":67109,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-21T00:10:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222421496\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456013175\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002270411\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Space Scumbag\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Space Scumbag said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice! Can\u0027t wait for it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSome suggestions.\u00A0Maybe make the bullet shells a bit smaller. And how are the sound effect?\u00A0Nothing to hear in the video.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd no new Blaster? Was hoping to see it. Maybe in the future. Anyways, great work guys, this mod\u00A0is getting really good.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nV8 has\u00A0been trying to get ahold of you about the E-11\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Space Scumbag","CreatedById":70411,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-21T00:18:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222421503\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456013447\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002267109\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022War Eagle 1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, War Eagle 1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nV8 has\u00A0been trying to get ahold of you about the E-11\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know. I just send him a pm.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSadly I have no working E-11. V8jester will be surpsised when he reads how I pulled it off in my video. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Shuudoushi","CreatedById":158575,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-21T01:01:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222421297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456005694\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022136093\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022V8jester\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, V8jester said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n0.3 Teaser\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/tKekkfN85ps?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis needs to be a sub-assembly on kerbalx, like yesterday \u0026gt;..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"V8jester","CreatedById":136093,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-21T03:34:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222421496\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456013175\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002270411\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Space Scumbag\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Space Scumbag said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice! Can\u0027t wait for it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSome suggestions.\u00A0Maybe make the bullet shells a bit smaller. And how are the sound effect?\u00A0Nothing to hear in the video.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd no new Blaster? Was hoping to see it. Maybe in the future. Anyways, great work guys, this mod\u00A0is getting really good.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Blaster is still in the works. Spanner has been remodeling it as the one from Propros had over 49K Poly\u0027s. So to save those with slower computers. He has brought that down to 1200 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd as far as sounds. We have tried to do them justice. There are 14 new sounds in the FPS folder this time around. The only reason we haven\u0027t released FPS yet is because Spanner just wont stop adding in new stuff. Trust me it\u0027ll be well worth the wait.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"War Eagle 1","CreatedById":67109,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-21T03:38:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222421805\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456025690\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022136093\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022V8jester\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, V8jester said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Blaster is still in the works. Spanner has been remodeling it as the one from Propros had over 49K Poly\u0027s. So to save those with slower computers. He has brought that down to 1200 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd as far as sounds. We have tried to do them justice. There are 14 new sounds in the FPS folder this time around. The only reason we haven\u0027t released FPS yet is because Spanner just wont stop adding in new stuff. Trust me it\u0027ll be well worth the wait.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt this rate we won\u0027t have anything for 0.4\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"V8jester","CreatedById":136093,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-22T17:28:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=